  <div id="text-content_c9c00e92-7127-4f08-93b5-097bc4ae9c65" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The <strong>Training Services Portal </strong>link allows users to <a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Training-Services-Portal-as-an-admin/ta-p/198" target="_blank">access the Training Services Portal</a>, which contains self-paced training resources on a variety of Canvas topics.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="ask_the_community_non_students" data-step-uuid="4c7f8665-00fe-45da-af73-521fcf25cad8">
    <h2 id="ask_the_community_non_students" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Ask the Community</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/300/918/original/dc5b4078-3968-418b-883b-bac61635e19c.png" srcset="" alt="Ask the Community" height="464" width="354">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8bb70040-4c4e-4e19-935b-8166a4a78c28" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The <strong>Ask the Community </strong>link<strong> </strong>allows users with an admin-, instructor-, TA-, or designer-based role to collaborate with other members of the Canvas community for answers to Canvas questions. This link directs to the <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/community/answers" target="_blank">Find Answers space in the Canvas Community</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="request_a_feature" data-step-uuid="5ef91afe-435b-4f43-89c4-15c4d7f9b4bf">
    <h2 id="request_a_feature" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Request a Feature</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/300/896/original/0f23c869-5a47-452a-9861-11ec384fef2e.png" srcset="" alt="Request a Feature" height="464" width="354">
